Installation:

    Linux: git clone git://github.com/mrxd/dotvim.git ~/.vim
    Windows: git clone git://github.com/mrxd/dotvim.git %HOMEDRIVE%

Linking

    Create a new .vimrc (linux) or _vimrc (windows) in your home directory with the contents:

    "Load the first file named 'vimrc' found in the runtimepath
    runtime vimrc

Switch to the `~/.vim` directory, and fetch submodules:

    cd ~/.vim
    git submodule update --init
